com.sun.tools.javac.v8.util
类 Name

java.lang.Object
  com.sun.tools.javac.v8.util.Name

public class Name
extends java.lang.Object

An abstraction for internal compiler strings. For efficiency reasons, GJC uses hashed strings that are stored in a common large buffer. Names represent unique hashable strings. Two names are equal if their indices are equal. Utf8 representation is used for storing names internally.
